{"about_the_game":"<i>You wake up on a small island with no company except the local animals and lapping waves.</i><br>Time to make yourself at home!<br><br><strong>Garden of the Sea</strong> is a chilled-out life sim where you play, craft, and explore at your own pace. Discover new islands and unlock the mysteries of the ocean and its inhabitants, or stay where you are and let things gently take their course. You\u2019ll be fine either way. There are no fail states here, just different ways to win. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887410/extras/featuresyay.png?t=1730307301\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cultivate your own garden, full of flowers and delicious veggies you can cook!<br></li><li>Build and upgrade your very own home, adding decorations and furnishings!</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887410/extras/Gots_DifferentGardens__1_.gif?t=1730307301\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Complete quests to make progress and unlock rewards!<br></li><li>Befriend and nurture local creatures \u2013 birds, fish and more!</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887410/extras/ezgif-4-07d74e2b96.gif?t=1730307301\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore the surrounding islands in your boat!<br></li><li>Become one with the world through the power of reactional music!</li></ul><br>...and a whole lot more!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887410/extras/ezgif-4-14758b838c.gif?t=1730307301\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Bamboozled","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2887410/2f009017082fb494a6037eb22b85a4075d9d0be0.jpg"},{"name":"Reef Mignon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2887410/fdf1533b182725895b555e9a79a1